Grand Hyatt Kuala Lumpur jobs vacancies 2021 for Front Office, Housekeeping, Security, IT, Sales & Marketing, F&B, Culinary, Stewarding.

### About
The luxurious 5-star Grand Hyatt Kuala Lumpur is located just next to the Kuala Lumpur Convention Center (KLCC).A 14-minute walk from the KLCC light rail station, this upscale hotel is 9 minutes' walk from the Petronas Towers.

